is now closed for the day.

07:41.995 --> 07:43.143
Sorry, no yay.

07:43.317 --> 07:46.340
But you can all feel free to 
enjoy the rest of the museum.

07:50.645 --> 07:51.743
Evolution?

08:00.626 --> 08:02.020
Excuse me.

08:02.146 --> 08:04.472
How can you put up an 
exhibit on the origin of

08:04.526 --> 08:06.712
man and not have one 
mention of the bible?

08:06.975 --> 08:07.620
We do.

08:09.895 --> 08:14.581
What a fool believes...

08:17.115 --> 08:19.681
my most cherished beliefs, a myth?

08:19.896 --> 08:21.610
Daddy, was mommy a monkey?

08:21.655 --> 08:22.943
I can't remember.

08:22.986 --> 08:24.851
No one was ever a monkey!

08:24.877 --> 08:26.920
Everything is what it was and always will be!

08:26.936 --> 08:28.683
God put us here and that's that.

08:29.076 --> 08:31.623
But you said a stork brought me.

08:31.685 --> 08:33.691
That was god disguised as a stork.

08:33.788 --> 08:35.350
Who brings baby storks?

08:35.356 --> 08:37.063
There's no such thing as storks!

08:37.095 --> 08:38.011
It's all god.

08:38.898 --> 08:40.470
Please bless daddy and mommy....

08:40.506 --> 08:42.561
stop praying to that stork!

08:46.155 --> 08:49.393
They're telling people we're 
descended from a pack of apes.

08:49.455 --> 08:51.511
Even though there's nothing 
about it in the bible.

08:51.626 --> 08:54.080
Ned, you've got to take this 
thing with a grain of salt.

08:54.118 --> 08:56.011
I mean, come on.

08:56.165 --> 08:59.731
Tim, this controversy could 
put more meat in the seats.

09:00.017 --> 09:02.901
Well... our membership has been dwindling

09:02.958 --> 09:06.381
