09:14.116 --> 09:16.330
They'll be hanging on your every word.

09:16.486 --> 09:19.042
I'll be a white Al Sharpton.

09:23.067 --> 09:25.870
Why does every church 
meeting end this way?

09:27.955 --> 09:31.791
We want you to teach alternative 
theories to Darwinian evolution.

09:31.986 --> 09:33.931
You mean lamarckian evolution?

09:34.107 --> 09:36.393
No, the Adam and Eve one.

09:36.656 --> 09:38.133
And what if I say no?

09:38.316 --> 09:41.943
I believe you leased your Camry 
from christian brothers auto.

09:42.105 --> 09:44.971
No! That was a once-in-a-lifetime APR!

09:45.005 --> 09:47.180
Class, starting today, we will be presenting

09:47.227 --> 09:49.660
an alternative theory on the origin of man.

09:53.075 --> 09:54.151
Creationism?!

09:54.525 --> 09:55.671
But that's not science.

09:56.187 --> 09:56.950
It is now.

09:57.035 --> 09:58.970
Are oceans god's tears?

10:02.305 --> 10:03.500
They sure are.

10:03.588 --> 10:04.663
A-plus.

10:05.895 --> 10:07.841
Now Lisa's the Ralph.

10:08.927 --> 10:12.663
How can you teach the book of 
genesis as a scientific theory?

10:13.366 --> 10:15.573
This helpful video will 
evade all your questions.

10:15.615 --> 10:17.242
Eyes screenward.

10:23.575 --> 10:25.443
Let's say hi to two books.

10:25.695 --> 10:28.811
One, the bible, was written by our lord.

10:32.235 --> 10:34.911
The other, "the origin of species,"

10:34.968 --> 10:38.410
