drunk named charles Darwin.

10:42.407 --> 10:43.562
This is slander.

10:43.622 --> 10:46.358
Darwin was one of the 
greatest minds of all time.

10:46.468 --> 10:49.094
Then why is he making out with satan?

10:51.908 --> 10:55.228
Evolution is widely 
acknowledged as scientific fact.

10:55.426 --> 10:57.760
It's even accepted by 
prominent conservatives

10:57.817 --> 11:00.662
like George will and the 
late pope John Paul.

11:01.485 --> 11:03.081
That's something to think about.

11:03.127 --> 11:04.560
The George will?

11:04.875 --> 11:06.521
Lisa, you've said quite enough.

11:06.686 --> 11:08.940
Children, drown her out with 
whistling and arm flatulence.

11:09.086 --> 11:10.603
All I'm saying is...

11:24.146 --> 11:25.662
What's wrong, sweetie?

11:25.788 --> 11:28.780
They're making us learn 
creation theory in school.

11:28.997 --> 11:32.623
Today we had a test, and 
every answer was "god did it."

11:33.156 --> 11:37.052
Well, I think it's good to 
give both ideas a fair hearing.

11:37.156 --> 11:38.740
Maybe they could learn from each other.

11:38.787 --> 11:41.033
But they're incompatible!

11:41.108 --> 11:45.770
Lisa, lots of times two incompatible 
things can both be true.

11:45.858 --> 11:49.501
My son's a brat, but 
he's a special little guy.

11:49.646 --> 11:53.491
You father says he's at work, but 
there he is jumping on a trampoline.

11:54.727 --> 11:58.812
Mom, you really have to choose 
here between science and belief.

12:03.847 --> 12:06.242
Well, then I choose...

12:15.916 --> 12:19.391
so, according to creationism, 
there were no cavemen.

12:19.495 --> 12:20.391
Good riddance.

12:20.448 --> 12:22.481
Their drawings suck and 
they look like hippies.

12:22.568 --> 12:25.771
Dad, you're not really 
reconsidering evolution, are you?

12:25.925 --> 12:28.713
My mind is always open to new ideas.

12:29.067 --> 12:29.653
Onions?!

12:29.817 --> 12:30.680
In the peas?!

12:30.797 --> 12:32.033
What the hell!

12:36.807 --> 12:37.813
It is agreed...

12:38.046 --> 12:40.601
regular people can park 
in handicapped spaces

12:40.836 --> 12:43.070
if they're just running in to buy smokes

12:43.276 --> 12:45.642
or maybe some pop tarts for tomorrow.

12:45.915 --> 12:47.390
The system works.

12:47.468 --> 12:49.642
And if there's no further business,

12:49.757 --> 12:52.951
I hereby declare this meeting...

12:53.026 --> 12:54.570
I have an issue I'd like to raise.

12:54.646 --> 12:56.352
Curse my slow gaveling.

12:56.386 --> 12:59.622
Last week, the unscientific 
theory of creationism

12:59.698 --> 13:03.752
was introduced alongside evolution 
in Springfield public schools.

13:04.766 --> 13:09.022
Now, honestly, the bible's about the 
same age as, the rest of our textbooks.

13:11.195 --> 13:14.572
Evolution and creationism 
cannot coexist, people.

13:14.726 --> 13:17.340
It is time to go back to 
teaching one single truth.

13:17.448 --> 13:20.352
Homer's son's sister's right.

13:23.195 --> 13:24.931
Class, the town has spoken.

13:25.027 --> 13:27.641
From now on we're only teaching one theory...

13:27.666 --> 13:28.643
creationism.

13:28.858 --> 13:31.961
Now please hand in your evolution 
books to groundskeeper Willie

13:32.137 --> 13:33.992
while I beat this ominous drum.

13:42.695 --> 13:44.950
There seems to be a note on your locker!

13:45.106 --> 13:46.993
From a secret admirer, perhaps.

13:47.657 --> 13:48.771
Don't make me laugh.

13:50.405 --> 13:52.133
"Dear seekers of truth:

13:52.377 --> 13:55.931
"Meet in the school's single-purpose 
room tomorrow at lunch.

13:56.128 --> 13:59.263
"Rationally yours, L.M.S."

13:59.576 --> 14:00.451
"L.M.S."

14:00.527 --> 14:01.852
Who could it be?

14:08.337 --> 14:09.512
Little Moe Szyslak?

14:10.405 --> 14:11.661
Why does everybody call me that?

14:11.955 --> 14:13.711
Bunch of snot-faced pukebags.

14:23.237 --> 14:24.862
I'm so glad you could all come.

14:24.915 --> 14:29.510
I will be reading to you from the 
original of species by Charles Darwin.

14:30.505 --> 14:32.842
I thought we're gonna light spiders on fire.

14:33.576 --> 14:34.540
We're over here.

14:39.518 --> 14:40.701
You all have a nice day.

14:43.697 --> 14:46.111
"Chapter one: When we compare the individuals

14:46.146 --> 14:47.201
"of the same variety

14:47.246 --> 14:50.793
"or sub-variety of our older 
cultivated plants and animals..."

14:52.067 --> 14:53.763
Lisa Simpson, you're under arrest

14:53.826 --> 14:56.230
for the teaching of non-biblical science!

14:58.465 --> 15:03.101
There are so many worse crimes. 
Why are you persecuting me?

15:03.177 --> 15:06.751
We only have the manpower to 
enforce the last law passed.

15:06.808 --> 15:08.330
You know, it's not the best system, but...

15:08.587 --> 15:10.592
well, in fact, it's...
it's pretty much the worst.

15:12.726 --> 15:14.272
you live! You die!

15:14.878 --> 15:16.423
You live! You die!

