Defending miss Simpson is aclu-appointed 
liberal, Clarisse Drummond.

15:32.447 --> 15:33.381
I'm from new york!

15:35.006 --> 15:37.192
And prosecuting the case against Lisa

15:37.208 --> 15:40.142
is humble country lawyer Wallace Brady.

15:40.386 --> 15:42.143
As the little chicken said to his mama,

15:42.346 --> 15:43.721
"I just hope I don't 'cluck up.'"

15:45.395 --> 15:48.131
I think it's fair to say 
if that man doesn't win,

15:48.378 --> 15:50.022
I'm resigning from the jury.

15:50.367 --> 15:53.182
This is Kent Brockman, juror 
number seven, saying,

15:53.627 --> 15:55.182
"I'll have the roast beef for lunch."

15:57.256 --> 16:01.282
So does this theory of evolution 
necessarily mean that there is no god?

16:01.435 --> 16:02.340
No, of course not.

16:03.737 --> 16:07.481
It just says that god is an 
impotent nothing from nowhere

16:07.516 --> 16:10.113
with less power than the 
undersecretary of agriculture,

16:10.155 --> 16:12.500
who has very little power in our system.

16:17.195 --> 16:19.761
Now, sir, you are a scientist, correct?

16:20.147 --> 16:24.003
That's right. I have a phd in 
truthology from christian tech.

16:25.718 --> 16:26.880
Move over, Carl.

16:26.936 --> 16:27.822
I got a new hero!

16:28.186 --> 16:29.750
Yeah, this'll last about a day.

16:30.268 --> 16:34.490
So, as a scientist, what is your 
take on this "devil-ution"?

16:35.767 --> 16:36.571
Pure hogwash.

16:36.866 --> 16:38.991
If man evolved from monkeys, 
there'd be evidence.

16:39.117 --> 16:42.051
But when we look at the fossil 
record, here's what we see.

16:42.565 --> 16:44.031
A missing link.

16:47.488 --> 16:50.293
Why, I believe, right now, 
this gentleman's having dinner

16:50.315 --> 16:52.083
with the tooth fairy and the easter bunny.

16:52.425 --> 16:55.272
This is the break in the 
case we've been waiting for!

16:55.505 --> 16:56.790
I mean, he doesn't exist.

16:57.075 --> 16:59.110
Evolution is just a lot 
of that hollywood hooey.

17:03.808 --> 17:05.079
Well, I've heard enough for today.

17:05.477 --> 17:07.452
I have to judge a wet t-shirt 
contest in 20 minutes.

17:07.656 --> 17:10.432
Ah, this trial is the biggest load of...

17:11.088 --> 17:12.463
For crying out loud!

17:12.808 --> 17:16.133
Now. Bambi, who started that 
forest fire that killed your mama?

17:16.906 --> 17:17.913
Evolution?!

17:18.358 --> 17:20.093
My, my, my.

17:20.415 --> 17:21.721
Poor bambi.

17:22.367 --> 17:23.663
Poor thumper...

17:30.667 --> 17:32.103
I'm sorry, mom.

17:32.117 --> 17:34.901
I should have just gone with 
the flow, like you said.

17:42.826 --> 17:45.463
Well, I might as well see 
what all the fuss is about.

17:56.716 --> 17:58.093
Homer, Homer, please.

17:58.456 --> 17:59.913
I love it when you're not into it.

17:59.955 --> 18:01.663
Oh, yeah, baby, mmm...

18:02.278 --> 18:03.141
That's it, ignore me.

18:03.307 --> 18:04.390
I'm not even here.

18:06.118 --> 18:09.573
