is incredibly persuasive,

18:09.747 --> 18:13.513
and his ship was the beagle, which 
reminds me of snoopy, my favorite peanut!

18:17.008 --> 18:20.283
Lisa, I thinI have a way to 
help you at the trial today.

18:20.656 --> 18:21.242
So do I!

18:22.868 --> 18:25.332
Milhouse will serve the time 
for you while you flee to Mexico.

18:25.538 --> 18:27.800
Your new name: Senorita Ugly.

18:28.545 --> 18:31.591
Honey, I appreciate the thought, 
but just leave everything to me.

18:32.905 --> 18:35.030
You can take off the wig, Mihouse.

18:35.225 --> 18:36.181
I'm Nelson!

18:46.245 --> 18:48.993
Now, Mr. Flanders, you're 
familiar with the bible, correct?

18:49.287 --> 18:51.521
As familiar as it's proper to be.

18:51.996 --> 18:53.053
Don't worry, Lisa.

18:53.347 --> 18:55.901
I've got the answer to 
your problems right here.

18:57.146 --> 18:59.531
Look, Homie, I brought you a beer.

18:59.685 --> 19:00.700
Thanks, Marge.

19:02.776 --> 19:03.710
It's not a twist-off!

19:05.108 --> 19:05.581
Come on!

19:09.195 --> 19:12.373
And you are positive that 
man and ape cannot be related?

19:12.587 --> 19:15.303
As sure as I am that Jesus hates hip-hop!

19:15.385 --> 19:16.733
Come on! Open!

19:16.885 --> 19:18.731
I want what's in you!

19:21.495 --> 19:21.930
As a matter...

19:21.935 --> 19:22.850
I want... you...

19:22.855 --> 19:23.352
Homer...

19:23.356 --> 19:23.721
stupid...

19:25.438 --> 19:26.261
Homer, I'm trying to...

19:29.947 --> 19:32.563
will you shut your yap, you 
big monkey-faced gorilla!

19:34.066 --> 19:36.351
Mr. Flanders, you've sworn 
to tell the truth.

19:36.638 --> 19:39.842
Can you say that this man could not 
possibly be related to that ape?

19:43.016 --> 19:43.781
You win, Lisa.

19:44.388 --> 19:46.110
This court hereby rules that the law

19:46.186 --> 19:48.771
forbidding the teaching 
of evolution is repealed.

19:52.067 --> 19:53.231
Wait, it was a twist-off.

19:55.826 --> 19:56.791
Thanks, mom.

19:57.186 --> 19:59.832
Thank you, honey, for opening my eyes.

20:00.088 --> 20:02.762
I can't wait to see what 
evolution will make next.

20:02.956 --> 20:06.710
Maybe a bird with a people 
face or a bear with pants on!

20:07.005 --> 20:08.271
Let's go, boys.

20:08.427 --> 20:10.163
Your poor old popsicle's been licked.

20:10.207 --> 20:11.371
Mr. Flanders, wait!

20:12.185 --> 20:14.611
I want you to know, 
I respect your beliefs,

20:14.666 --> 20:16.722
and I can see how deeply you feel about them.

20:17.008 --> 20:19.631
I just don't think religion 
should be taught in our schools,

20:19.728 --> 20:22.870
any more than you'd want 
scientist teaching at the church.

20:23.365 --> 20:26.072
Well, i wish this world 
would evolve a few more

20:26.137 --> 20:27.250
kids like you, Lisa.

20:27.665 --> 20:32.021
What say we take our worthy 
adversary out for a hot fudge fun-day?

20:32.337 --> 20:33.711
Cram it, ya god wad.

